    <h2 class="w-h2">One SDK. Every prediction market&nbsp;vertical.</h2>
    <p class="w-lead">We built this SDK because we trade these markets ourselves. Weather is the first vertical we ship. Every vertical that follows gets the same depth: the same source discipline, the same settlement-grade accuracy, and the same agent-ready schemas. We only ship a vertical when we understand it well enough to trade&nbsp;it.</p>

